I"¥<p>The first version of <code class="highlighter-rouge">binomen</code> is now up on <a href="https://cran.rstudio.com/web/packages/binomen">CRAN</a>. It provides various taxonomic classes for defining a single taxon, multiple taxa, and a taxonomic data.frame. It is designed as a companion to <a href="https://github.com/ropensci/taxize">taxize</a>, where you can get taxonomic data on taxonomic names from the web.</p>

